CERTIFICATE OF APPROVAL

 
 I, Hilda a. Manual____________ , Deputy Commissioner of Indian Affairs, by virtue of the
authority granted to the Secretary of the Interior by the Indian Reorganization Act of June 
18, 1934 (48 Stat. 984), as amended, and delegated to me by Secretarial Order No. 3150 
as extended by Secretarial Order No. 3177, as amended, do hereby approve the 
Constitution of the Little River Band of Ottawa. This Constitution is effective as of this 
